<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hesitate-vi">hesitate <strong><em>vi</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'hezɪteɪt/    美 /'hezɪteɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>踌躇；犹豫；顾虑：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He hesitated before he replied.
回答前，他犹豫了一下。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 7</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>hesitate to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I hesitate to tell you the truth.
我不大想告诉你真相。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you need any help, don't hesitate to call us.
如果你需要帮助，随时给我们打电话。</p><footer>外研① – 6</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don't hesitate to ask me if you have any questions.
如果你有任何问题，随时问我。</p><footer>2017 全国书面表达</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>hesitate about / over:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She hesitated about / over the choice between the two dresses.
她对到底选择这两件衣服中的哪一件犹豫不决。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>We are at your service. Don’t hesitate <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (turn) to us if you have any further problems.  （2009 福建改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. to turn  </p></div>